headline: Aptiv Reports First Quarter 2025 Financial Results
summary: SCHAFFHAUSEN, Switzerland, May 01, 2025--Aptiv PLC (NYSE: APTV), a global technology company focused on making the world safer, greener and more connected, today reported a first quarter 2025 U.S. GAAP loss of $0.05 per diluted share. Excluding special items, first quarter earnings totaled $1.69 per diluted share.
